The second likely category is cs.SD (Software Development), as the paper proposes a new algorithm for community extraction in social networks. The third likely category is cs.SOC (Computational Social Science), which deals with the application of computational methods to social science research. The fourth likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as the paper proposes a new measure and algorithm for community extraction.
